            "summary": "In this video, we chat with Karel-Oscar van Hengel, the Founder of HyperTalented, which is a staffing and recruiting agency.\u00a0 Karel-Oscar, or \u201cKO\u201d for short, is a Dutch Entrepreneur living in Paris and Amsterdam.\u00a0 "
